### Run test locally
POST http://localhost:1234/test/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "serviceName": "{{serviceName}}",
    "token": "{{token}}",
    "ratePerSecond": 5000,
    "testCount": 500000,
    "processingTimeMillis": 1000,
    "accounts": "acc-13"
}

### Stop running test to save time and resources
# @timeout 120
POST http://localhost:1234/test/stop/{{serviceName}}